    <item>
      <title>如果确认领导财政部，Bessent 将出售对冲基金股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/bessent-to-sell-hedge-fund-stake-if-confirmed-to-lead-treasury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的美国财政部部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）如果得到参议院的批准，将辞去 Key Square Group 的职务并出售其在合伙企业中的股份，以避免利益冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/bessent-to-sell-hedge-fund-stake-if-confirmed-to-lead-treasury</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 21:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普调查结束，特别检察官杰克·史密斯辞去司法部职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/special-counsel-jack-smith-resigns-from-doj-as-trump-probes-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据政府周六提交的法庭文件显示，杰克·史密斯已辞去负责监督当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的联邦刑事调查的特别顾问职务，并已“脱离”美国司法部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/special-counsel-jack-smith-resigns-from-doj-as-trump-probes-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 21:29:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在任期即将结束时向教皇授予总统勋章</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/biden-awards-pope-a-presidential-medal-in-waning-days-of-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登向教皇方济各颁发总统自由勋章，这是他罗马天主教信仰的个人标志，此前加州发生的毁灭性火灾导致总统在任期的最后几天取消了对梵蒂冈的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/biden-awards-pope-a-presidential-medal-in-waning-days-of-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 20:42:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对派领袖宣布返回后将发起新的抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/mozambique-opposition-chief-declares-fresh-protests-after-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对派领导人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 呼吁下周再次发起抗议活动，这将与该国新当选总统丹尼尔·查波 (Daniel Chapo) 的就职典礼发生冲突，从而再次加剧十月选举后的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/mozambique-opposition-chief-declares-fresh-protests-after-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 19:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国保守派担心特朗普可能破坏胜利之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/german-conservatives-fret-trump-could-disrupt-path-to-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守派担心唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫可能会影响他们在选举中击败德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/german-conservatives-fret-trump-could-disrupt-path-to-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 18:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
