      <title>埃塞俄比亚、索马里领导人举行会晤同意恢复关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/ethiopia-somalia-leaders-meet-agree-to-restore-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚总理阿比·艾哈迈德和索马里总统哈桑·谢赫·穆罕默德周六在亚的斯亚贝巴举行会晤，深化了上个月在土耳其斡旋下达成的和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/ethiopia-somalia-leaders-meet-agree-to-restore-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 18:12:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
