      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 17:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶大火向东北方向蔓延，威胁贝莱尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毁灭性的帕利塞兹大火向东北方向推进，在短暂的喘息之后，更多干燥风的威胁加剧了风险，迫使南加州极其富裕的布伦特伍德和贝莱尔社区重新进行疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 12:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨加强对特朗普扩张主义言论的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/scholz-derides-cdu-tax-plans-as-attack-on-germany-s-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨在一次激动人心的演讲中加大了对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在边界完整性问题上的批评，旨在为下个月的联邦选举前激励社会民主党人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/scholz-derides-cdu-tax-plans-as-attack-on-germany-s-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 11:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大力推广与中国的交易，里夫斯力图平息市场动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/reeves-seeks-to-calm-market-turmoil-as-uk-touts-china-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 访华期间试图缓解市场对政府财政状况的担忧，她在中国与英国达成了未来五年将为英国经济带来价值 6 亿英镑（7.31 亿美元）的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/reeves-seeks-to-calm-market-turmoil-as-uk-touts-china-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 11:19:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
